  "subject": "Test: Test new fetch from Gerrit ability",
  "commit_message": "Test: Test new fetch from Gerrit ability\n\nA new feature has been added to the gerrit checkout action that is\nsupposed to try checking out the change directly from Gerrit if it fails\nto get it from the GitHub mirror. This puts a job in place in an\nadvisory position to allow us to validate over time if this is working\ncorrectly.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Idabf008cc4e6f29190714cd606e4475936640c2f\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Grimberg <agrimberg@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
